               <interp inst="t17750531-1-person223" type="surname" value="Perreau"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750531-1-person223" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750531-1-person223" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             about seven years; I live next door to him: he is a very honest worthy man, and very well respected by every body.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17750531-1-person224">
                  William
                   Hocker
               <interp inst="t17750531-1-person224" type="surname" value="Hocker"></interp>
