                  </persName>
             five or six years. He is a very honest man as any in the neighbourhood; a man that any body will do any thing for. He is very well respected.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17750531-1-person227">
                  Richard
                   Brown
               <interp inst="t17750531-1-person227" type="surname" value="Brown"></interp>
